headline: Earnings, existing home sales, Hinge Health IPO: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime hosts Julie Hyman and Josh Lipton preview the biggest stories and headlines expected out tomorrow, Thursday, May 22, including earnings results out from Williams-Sonoma (WSM), Ralph Lauren (RL), Intuit (INTU), Workday (WDAY), Ross Stores (ROST), and Deckers Outdoors (DECK); commentary from Federal Reserve Bank of New York President John Williams; US existing home sales data, and the IPO of Hinge Health (HNGE). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
